<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Secret-Key on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/secret-key/</link><description>Recent content in Secret-Key on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/secret-key/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Config error: key not set</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/config-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/config-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when Flask cannot find a required configuration key. This commonly happens with &lt;code&gt;SECRET_KEY&lt;/code&gt;, database URLs, or other critical settings that are expected but not loaded.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;SECRET_KEY&lt;/code&gt; not set or not loaded from environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Environment variable not available in the deployment environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; file or &lt;code&gt;python-dotenv&lt;/code&gt; not loaded&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Configuration class or file not properly imported&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load configuration from environment variables:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; os
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; os&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;environ&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;dev-key-change-me&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;python-dotenv&lt;/code&gt; to load a &lt;code&gt;.env&lt;/code&gt; file:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; dotenv &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; load_dotenv
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; os
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;load_dotenv()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; os&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;environ&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Load from a Python config file:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;from_object(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;config.ProductionConfig&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use a separate config class:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Config&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; SECRET_KEY &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; os&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;environ&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;unsafe&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URI &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; os&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;environ&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;get(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;DATABASE_URL&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;ProductionConfig&lt;/span&gt;(Config):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; DEBUG &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;False&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;from_object(ProductionConfig)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;app &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; Flask(__name__)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;@app.route&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/secret&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;def&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;secret&lt;/span&gt;():
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; app&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;config[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# KeyError if not set&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;KeyError: &amp;#39;SECRET_KEY&amp;#39;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/flask/blueprint-error/"&gt;Blueprint registration error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>